The '''Third Quadrant''' was one of the divisions of the [[Zi-Kree Sector]] of the [[Ecumenopolis/Legends|ecumenopolis]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. The infamous [[Crimson Corridor]] was located in Zi-Kree's Third Quadrant.

[[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Darsha Assant]] was sent to the quadrant around [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]] to escort the [[Black Sun/Legends|Black Sun]] defector [[Oolth]] back to the [[Jedi Temple/Legends|Jedi Temple]].

